headline: How NextEra Energy’s Post-Inflation Data Rally Impacts Its 2025 Valuation Outlook
summary: Thinking about what to do with your NextEra Energy shares? You are far from alone right now. With the stock closing recently at $78.67 and notching a 6.6% gain over just the past week, investors are clearly reacting to shifting sentiment around utilities and clean energy.
